s</span>(xlValue).<span class=\"hljs-property\">DisplayUnitLabel</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(displayUnitLabel.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Characters</span>(<span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Text</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
